# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Description
# -----------
#
# Use Emacs PEL facilities to start Emacs in terminal mode, log its startup
# time and then turn Emacs off.
#
# Requirements:  e :
#                - a script or shell alias that starts Emacs in terminal mode.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Script
# ------
#
#
e -e pel-log-init-time -e kill-emacs

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
